      "content": "Hey, I'm planning a solo trip to Chicago next month and wanted to get some advice. I'm looking for a neighborhood that feels really safe, upscale, and has a nice sense of community. Given the current social climate and everything in the news, which specific areas should I probably avoid so I don't run into any trouble or bad vibes while I'm walking around?",
